OL,4,CFirms urged to give staff time off for
OL,5,CEngland game
OL,6, Staff should be allowed to finish work
OL,7, early to watch England take on Germany,
OL,8, Sir Keir Starmer has said.
OL,10,FThe Labour leader's comments come after
OL,11,Fthe Trade Union Congress (TUC) urged
OL,12,Femployers to be flexible in allowing
OL,13,Fworkers time off to follow the Euro
OL,14,F2020 clash, which starts at 17:00 BST.
OL,16,FTUC general secretary Frances O'Grady
OL,17,Fsaid bosses being flexible can cut
OL,18,Fabsences and boost productivity.
OL,20,FShe added staff could make up any lost
OL,21,Ftime at a later date.
